<lb ed="X" n="0993a01"/><lg id="lgX26p0993a0101"><l>陷溺沉迷<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>有年</l><l>愛河瀼瀼浪<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">滔</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">淊</rdg></app>天</l>
